    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/a21d11b3002725480754983a25637d69.avif?t=1679587256\" width=616 height=159 /></span><br><br>Being an adult sucks! Life was so much easier when Akiko was saving the world with her magical girl squad, the Sentinels of Justice. Now she’s stuck working a boring retail job, watching the days creep closer to Y2K. She’s lost touch with her high school friends, her powers, and herself. Worst of all...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAGIC IS DISAPPEARING</h2>When Akiko realizes her healing magic is fading, she knows it's a sign of trouble. But things only get worse from there — her old teammates are affected too and soon the greater populace of the city! As Akiko, with help from the Sentinels, track down what's happening to magic (and who might be behind it) before it's too late.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/ca92c0f123cc66c4b8a0b082087bc7ff.apng?t=1679587256\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/ca92c0f123cc66c4b8a0b082087bc7ff.poster.avif?t=1679587256\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=406 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the Sentinels</h2>Reconnect with your former teammates! All the Sentinels have moved on from magical girl life in their own way. Spend your free time getting closer to them (and even finding love!) with optional routes between your work day and your magical girl sleuthing.<br><br><br>But the Sentinels aren't the only ones you'll meet! Hang out with your Glamour Pop work wife and avoid running into your ex, Solaire Blaze (don't even get us started!).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/a07e5a727ec4ff0b7020ad9fd80b4616.poster.avif?t=1679587256\" width=616 height=237 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/a07e5a727ec4ff0b7020ad9fd80b4616.webm?t=1679587256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Go to Work!?</h2>Even former magical girls have to pay rent! Go to your shift at Glamour Pop: the high-end, low-paying retail job that you got after high school. Deal with the demands of the customers and if successful, you might just have more energy to hang with your friends! Plus, you wouldn't want to get on the bad side of Glamour Pop's CEO Anna Lee…<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/b85608c0dec8713138d1e9a3fd0970e1.avif?t=1679587256\" width=616 height=159 /></span><br><br>Life After Magic is a queer, retro visual novel featuring:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>    100k+ words<br></li><li>    13 tracks of original music<br></li><li>    Handmade pixel art, CGs &amp; VFX<br></li><li>    Sapphic main cast with lots to discover about each character<br></li><li>    Optional routes for friendship and romance (and a secret or two!)<br></li><li>    Workplace mini-game and one special ending mini-game<br></li><li>    Y2K anxiety<br></li><li>    A funky li'l cat</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/9d32b0a0162447f5cd27a3f40777fb8a.poster.avif?t=1679587256\" width=616 height=225 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/9d32b0a0162447f5cd27a3f40777fb8a.webm?t=1679587256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Developed by</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332130/extras/08b007d271610c63f337cc277c784591.avif?t=1679587256\" width=616 height=150 /></span>",
